{"name": "bqplot-image-gl", "metadata": {"name": "bqplot-image-gl", "version": "1.5.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: IPython", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "Intended Audience :: Science/Research", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Topic :: Multimedia :: Graphics"], "home_page": "https://github.com/glue-viz/bqplot-image-gl", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["ipywidgets", "bqplot", "pillow"], "summary": "An ipywidget image widget for astronomical purposes", "upload_time": 1728987347}, "documentation": ["An ipywidget image widget for astronomical purposes\n"], "modules": [{"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.drag_events", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.mouse_events", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.keyboard_events", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector", "bases": ["BrushSelector"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector._view_module", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector._model_module", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector._view_module_version", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector._model_module_version", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector.pixel_aspect", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector.style", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector.border_style", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector._view_name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.BrushEllipseSelector._model_name", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["BrushEllipse interval selector interaction.\n\nThis 2-D selector interaction enables the user to select an ellipse\nregion using the brushing action of the mouse. A mouse-down marks the\ncenter of the ellipse. The drag after the mouse down selects a point\non the ellipse, drawn with the same aspect ratio as the change in x and y\nas measured in pixels. If pixel_aspect is set, the aspect ratio of the ellipse\nwill be used instead. Note that the aspect ratio is respected in the view\nwhere the ellipse is drawn.\n\nOnce an ellipse is drawn, it can be moved dragging, or reshaped by dragging\nthe border.\n\nThe selected_x and selected_y arrays define the bounding box of the ellipse.\n\n# Attributes\n\nselected_x: numpy.ndarray\n\n: Two element array containing the start and end of the interval selected\n  in terms of the x_scale of the selector.\n  This attribute changes while the selection is being made with the\n  `BrushSelector`.\n\nselected_y: numpy.ndarray\n\n: Two element array containing the start and end of the interval selected\n  in terms of the y_scale of the selector.\n  This attribute changes while the selection is being made with the\n  `BrushEllipseSelector`.\n\nbrushing: bool (default: False)\n\n: boolean attribute to indicate if the selector is being dragged.\n  It is True when the selector is being moved and False when it is not.\n  This attribute can be used to trigger computationally intensive code\n  which should be run only on the interval selection being completed as\n  opposed to code which should be run whenever selected is changing.\n"]}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction", "bases": ["Interaction"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction._view_module", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction._model_module", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction._view_module_version", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction._model_module_version", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction._view_name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction._model_name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction.x_scale", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction.y_scale", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction.cursor", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction.move_throttle", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction.next", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.interacts.MouseInteraction.events", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Mouse events listener.\n\nListen for mouse events on the kernel side.\nThe attributes 'x_scale' and 'y_scale' should be provided.\n\nEvent being passed are\n    * dragstart\n    * dragmove\n    * dragend\n    * click\n    * dblclick\n\nAll events are passed by a custom event with the following spec:\n`{event: <name>, pixel: {x: <pixel x>, y: <pixel y>}, domain: {x: <x>, y: <y>}} `\n\nPixel coordinates might be useful for debugging, domain coordinates should be used only.\n\nAttributes\n----------\nx_scale: An instance of Scale\n    This is the scale which is used for inversion from the pixels to data\n    co-ordinates in the x-direction.\ny_scale: An instance of Scale\n    This is the scale which is used for inversion from the pixels to data\n    co-ordinates in the y-direction.\nmove_throttle: Send mouse move events only every specified milliseconds."]}], "exports": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener", "bases": ["widgets.DOMWidget"], "methods": [{"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener._on_custom_msg", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "widget", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "content", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "buffers", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener._view_name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener._model_name", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener._view_module", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener._model_module", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener._view_module_version", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener._model_module_version", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener.widget", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener.css_selector", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "bqplot_image_gl.viewlistener.ViewListener.view_data", "type": n